          </li>
          <li>
            <threshold>8</threshold>
            <label>Collector's bag study complete</label>
            <text>{PAWN_nameDef} has completed {PAWN_possessive} studying. {PAWN_pronoun} finds a way to open the pocket dimension associated with it. Order someone to peruse them.</text>
          </li>
        </studyNotes>
      </li>
